The explosion breached the room!

4
00:01:48,826 --> 00:01:49,466
There's no time.

5
00:01:49,466 --> 00:01:50,347
- Wu!
- To the passage.

6
00:01:50,347 --> 00:01:52,386
This isn't what you meant
