Move it!

9
00:02:03,947 --> 00:02:04,906
Wu!

10
00:02:05,627 --> 00:02:06,546
Wu, hurry!

11
00:02:14,106 --> 00:02:14,787
Move!

12
00:02:14,787 --> 00:02:15,146
Okay.

13
00:02:15,586 --> 00:02:16,307
Pangzi, let's go.

14
