24
00:04:56,627 --> 00:04:57,427
Wu Xie!

25
00:04:58,026 --> 00:04:59,107
Wu Xie!

26
00:05:01,947 --> 00:05:02,586
Wu Xie!

27
00:05:04,547 --> 00:05:05,346
You okay?

28
00:05:05,346 --> 00:05:06,067
I'm fine.

29
00:05:06,947 --> 00:05:07,667
I'm fine.

30
00:05:07,747 --> 00:05:08,507
Where's Xiaoge?

31
00:05:11,867 --> 00:05:12,466
Alright.

32
00:05:12,706 --> 00:05:13,667
I'll find the exit.

33
00:05:14,146 --> 00:05:15,346
No, Pangzi!

34
00:05:36,826 --> 00:05:38,266
Pangzi, over here.

35
00:05:41,466 --> 00:05:42,187
Wu.

36
00:05:44,667 --> 00:05:46,146
This door won't budge.

37
00:05:47,586 --> 00:05:48,547
We need equal pressure

38
00:05:48,547 --> 00:05:50,507
