83
00:11:57,547 --> 00:11:58,746
Come on.

84
00:12:02,787 --> 00:12:03,547
Sit properly.

85
00:12:03,547 --> 00:12:04,147
Doctor!

86
00:12:04,147 --> 00:12:05,427
Doctor!

87
00:12:05,706 --> 00:12:06,466
He's awake.

88
00:12:18,626 --> 00:12:19,506
How is he?

89
00:12:19,866 --> 00:12:20,746
Looks good.

90
00:12:21,067 --> 00:12:21,866
In a couple of days,

91
00:12:21,866 --> 00:12:22,746
