92
00:12:22,746 --> 00:12:24,387
Good. That's good.

93
00:12:24,947 --> 00:12:25,466
Thank you.

94
00:12:25,626 --> 00:12:26,307
My pleasure.

95
00:12:27,027 --> 00:12:28,626
